OL,3,CWater supplies restored to Cardiff
OL,4,Carea after burst water main
OL,6,FWater supplies have now been restored
OL,7,Fto areas in Cardiff following a burst
OL,8,Fwater main.
OL,10,FTeams from Dwr Cymru Welsh Water
OL,11,Fworked throughout Wednesday night to
OL,12,Frestore the supplies to the Llanrumney
OL,13,Fand St Mellons areas.
OL,15,FBottled water supplies will remain
OL,16,Fopen on Thursday morning at Eastern
OL,17,FLeisure Centre in Llanrumney and Tesco
OL,18,Fin St Mellons.
