OL,3,CWater supplies restored to Cardiff
OL,4,Carea after burst water main
OL,6,FA statement from the company said:
OL,7,F"Our teams have worked overnight to
OL,8,Ffix the burst water main and supply
OL,9,Fbottled water to over 700 vulnerable
OL,10,Fcustomers.
OL,12,F"The burst water main has now been
OL,13,Ffixed and water supplies are now
OL,14,Frestored due to rezoning and tankering
OL,15,Foperations.
OL,17,F"We are in the process of re-filling
OL,18,Fthe network but this needs to be done
OL,19,Fcarefully and slowly to avoid any
OL,20,Ffurther bursts.
